thread.title: Cocoa Futures Rally to 18-Month High

author: Benjamin Parkin
title: Cocoa Futures Rally to 18-Month High

organizations.name: cocoa futures rally to 18-month high cocoa

text:
Cocoa futures started the week with a bounce, rising to the highest point in a year and a half.
Prices had rallied for several months on expectations of tighter supply out of West Africa and better demand in Europe and elsewhere, before stumbling in late March.
